 was still in the field there.|date=2 November 2011|work=Dawn News}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://nation.com.pk/20-Jan-2012/no-military-operation-in-balochistan?show=566|title=No military operation in Balochistan|accessdate=19 April 2019|work=Nation}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1041117|title=No army operation in Balochistan: Kayani|date=7 September 2013|work=Dawn News|quote='Not a single soldier of Pakistan Army is involved in any operation in Balochistan,' Gen Kayani said.}}</ref>)}}\n* [[Inter-Services Intelligence]]\n* [[Paramilitary forces of Pakistan|Paramilitary Forces]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1354086|title=FC accelerates intelligence-based operations in Balochistan|date=27 August 2017|work=Dawn News}}</ref>\n* [[Law enforcement in Pakistan|Police Forces]]\n'''{{flag|Iran}}'''<ref>{{cite news\n   | title = Jundallah: Profile Of A Sunni Extremist Group\n   | author = Abubakar Siddique\n   | publisher = Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty\n   | url = http://www.rferl.org/content/Jundallah_Profile_Of_A_Sunni_Extremist_Group/1856699.html\n   | date = 20 October 2009\n }}</ref>\n* [[Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps|IRGC]] {{small|(since 1980)}}\n* [[Islamic Republic of Iran Border Guard Command|Border Guard]] {{small|(since 2000)}}\n{{flagicon|Iran|1964}} [[Imperial State of Iran]] {{small|(until 1979)}}<ref>{{cite news\n   | title = Jundallah: Profile Of A Sunni Extremist Group\n   | author = Abubakar Siddique\n   | publisher = Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty\n   | url = http://www.rferl.org/content/Jundallah_Profile_Of_A_Sunni_Extremist_Group/1856699.html\n   | date = 20 October 2009\n }}</ref>\n* [[Military history of Iran#Pahlavi Era (1925 to 1979)|Imperial Iranian Army]]\n| combatant2        = '''[[Baloch nationalism|Baloch separatist groups]]'''\n* {{flagicon image|Balochistan Flag.png}} [[Baloch Republican Army|BRA]]\n* [[Baluch Liberation Front|BLF]]\n* [[United Baloch Army|UBA]]\n* [[Lashkar-e-Balochistan|LeB]