cite book|title=Dynamics of Political Development in Afghanistan: The British, Russian, and American Invasions|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0UzJAAAAQBAJ&dq|date=18 October 2010|last=Emadi|first=H.|pages=94\u201395|publisher=Springer}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Pakistan's Inter-Services Intelligence Directorate: Covert Action and Internal Operations|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SzGTDAAAQBAJ&dq|date=1 July 2016|publisher=Routledge|last=Sirrs|first=Owen L.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Faith, Unity, Discipline: The Inter-Service-Intelligence (ISI) of Pakistan|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=y_cgDgAAQBAJ&dq|date=15 November 2016|publisher=Oxford University Press|last=Kiessling|first=Hein}}</ref>\n----\n'''Sectarian groups'''\n*[[Jundallah (Iran)|Jundallah]] {{small|(2003\u201312)}}<ref>{{cite web\n   | title = Iran Offers Short-Term  Solutions To Long-Term  Problems Of Baluch Minority\n   | last = Aryan | first = Hossein\n   | publisher = Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty\n   | url = http://www.rferl.org/content/Iran_Offers_ShortTerm_Solutions_To_LongTerm_Problems_Of_Baluch_Minority/1858243.html\n   | date = 22 October 2009\n }}</ref><ref>{{cite news\n   | title = Iranian group makes kidnap claim \u2013 Middle East\n   | publisher = Al Jazeera\n   | url = http://english.aljazeera.net/video/middleeast/2010/10/2010101016024116222.html\n   | date = 10 October 2010\n }}</ref>\n*{{flagicon image|Flag of Jaish al-Adl.svg}} [[Jaish ul-Adl]] {{small|(since 2012)}}\n*{{flagicon image|AQMI Flag asymmetric.svg}} [[Jundallah (Pakistan)|Jundallah]] {{small|(since 1996)}}\n*{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg}} [[Al-Qaeda]] {{small|(since 1988)}}\n*{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg}} [[Lashkar-e-Jhangvi]] {{small|(since 1996)}}<ref name=h/>\n*{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg}} [[Sipah-e-Sahaba Pakistan|Sipah-e-Sahaba]] {{small|(since 1985)}}<ref name=h/>}}\n| commander1        = {{plainlist|\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] '''[[Arif Alvi]]'''<br />(2018\u2013present)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Mamnoon Hussain]]<br />(2013\u201318)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Asif Ali Zardari]]<br />(2008\u201313)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Pervez Musharraf]]<br />(2001\u201308)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Muhammad Rafiq Tarar]]<br />(1998\u201301)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Farooq Leghari]]<br />(1993\u201397)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Ghulam Ishaq Khan]]<br />(1988\u201393)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Muhammad Zia-ul-Haq]]<br />(1978\u201388)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Fazal Ilahi Chaudhry]]<br />(1973\u201378)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Zulfikar Ali Bhutto]]<br />(1971\u201373)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Yahya Khan]] <br /> (1969\u201371)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Ayub Khan (President of Pakistan)|Ayub Khan]] <br /> (1958\u201369)\n*[[File:Flag of the President of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Iskander Mirza]] <br /> (1956\u201358)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] '''[[Imran Khan]]''' <br /> (2018\u2013present)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Shahid Khaqan Abbasi]] <br /> (2017\u201318)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Nawaz Sharif]] <br /> (2013\u201317\u20131990\u201393\u20131997\u201399)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Raja Pervaiz Ashraf]] <br /> (2012\u201313)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Yousaf Raza Gillani]] <br /> (2008\u201312)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Shaukat Aziz]] <br /> (2004\u201307)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Pakistan.svg|25px]] [[Shujaat Hussain]] <br /> (until 26 August 2004)\n*[[File:Flag of the Prime 